contrail          contrail-vrouter-masters-2nqp6            3/3     Running            0                80m
jcnr              kube-crpd-worker-ds-vd7jn                 1/1     Running            0                48m
jcnr              syslog-ng-c4f7b7455-hxvgl                 1/1     Running            0                83m
kube-system       calico-kube-controllers-5f4fd8666-x2q99   1/1     Running            869 (2m1s ago)   46h
