    </section>
    <section id="section_zmf_mnh_xvb">
      <title>Downgrade to an Older Version</title>
      <p>For JCNR release 23.3, there is no procedure for downgrading to an older version. To change
        from a current version to an older version, you must uninstall the current version and
        install an older version.</p>
    </section>
